      "code_snippet": "\n// --- Case 1: classic off-by-one (linear, guard extractable) ----------------\n//   i in 0..10 -> a[10] escapes [0,9].  REAL overflow.\nint off_by_one(void)\n{\n    int a[10];\n    int s = 0;\n    for (int i = 0; i <= 10; i++)\n        s += a[i];\n    return s;\n}\n"
